==================================
The Rolling Hough Transform (RHT)
==================================

This is the Rolling Hough Transform, described in Clark, Peek, Putman 2014 (arXiv:1312.1338).

==================================
Requirements
==================================
Python 2.7
numpy
scipy
astropy
math
copy
matplotlib

